          </p>

          <div class="buttons">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href={`tel:${phoneHref}`}>Call for a Free Estimate</a>
            <a class="btn btn-secondary" href="#services">View Services</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card">
          <img src={logo} alt="Lakeside Landscaping LLC logo" width="118" height="118" />
          <h2>Reliable Outdoor Property Care</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>✓ Free estimates</li>
            <li>✓ Residential and commercial properties</li>
            <li>✓ Lawn mowing and routine maintenance</li>
            <li>✓ Planting, trimming, and cleanup work</li>
            <li>✓ Leaf removal and snow removal</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="services">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Our Services</h2>
          <p>
            Lakeside Landscaping LLC provides dependable outdoor services for lawns, yards,
            planting beds, seasonal cleanups, and winter weather needs.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid">
          <div class="card">
            <h3>Lawn Mowing</h3>
            <p>Routine lawn mowing, edging, trimming, and blowing for a clean, maintained property.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Landscaping Projects</h3>
            <p>Landscape refreshes, yard improvements, mulch, soil, planting beds, and general outdoor project work.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Hardscaping</h3>
            <p>Outdoor improvements such as stone, edging, walkways, and similar property upgrades.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Weeding & Trimming</h3>
            <p>Weeding, trimming, hedge care, shrub shaping, and cleanup around landscaped areas.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Planting</h3>
            <p>Planting flowers, shrubs, and greenery to improve the look of your outdoor space.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Leaf Removal & Cleanups</h3>
            <p>Seasonal cleanups, fall leaf removal, yard debris removal, and property cleanup services.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Snow Removal</h3>
            <p>Snow removal services to help keep residential and commercial properties accessible in winter.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Residential Service</h3>
            <p>Lawn and landscaping care for homeowners looking for reliable property maintenance.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="card">
            <h3>Commercial Service</h3>
            <p>Outdoor maintenance and seasonal services for businesses and commercial properties.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="process" class="process">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Simple, Reliable Service</h2>
          <p>
            We make it easy to request help, review the work needed, and schedule dependable
            outdoor property care.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="process-grid">
          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">1</div>
            <h3>Reach Out</h3>
            <p>Call, text, or email with the service you need and where the property is located.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">2</div>
            <h3>Free Estimate</h3>
            <p>We review the property needs and provide a clear estimate for the requested work.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">3</div>
            <h3>Schedule Work</h3>
            <p>Once approved, we schedule the project, cleanup, lawn care, or snow removal service.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="process-step">
            <div class="step-number">4</div>
            <h3>Clean Finish</h3>
            <p>We focus on neat work, clear communication, and leaving the property looking better.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="gallery" class="gallery">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Project Gallery</h2>
          <p>View recent landscaping, cleanup, mulch, lawn mowing, and property maintenance work.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="portfolio-slider" id="project-slideshow">
          <div class="slider-stage">
            <button class="slider-arrow prev" type="button" aria-label="Previous photo">‹</button>

            <div class="slider-window">
              <a class="main-slide-link" id="main-slide-link" href={galleryImages[0].src} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                <img
                  id="main-slide-image"
                  src={galleryImages[0].src}
                  alt={galleryImages[0].alt}
                  loading="eager"
                  decoding="async"
                  fetchpriority="high"
                />
              </a>
            </div>

            <button class="slider-arrow next" type="button" aria-label="Next photo">›</button>
          </div>

          <div class="slider-bottom">
            <div>
              <div class="slide-title" id="slide-title">{galleryImages[0].title}</div>
              <div class="slide-description" id="slide-description">{galleryImages[0].description}</div>
              <div class="slide-count" id="slide-count">Photo 1 of {galleryImages.length}</div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="dot-row" aria-label="Gallery photo selector">
            {galleryImages.map((image, index) => (
              <button
                class={`dot ${index === 0 ? "active" : ""}`}
                type="button"
                aria-label={`View ${image.title}`}
                data-slide-index={index}
              ></button>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="gallery-note">
          More completed project photos will be added as new work is finished.
        </p>

        <script type="application/json" id="gallery-data" set:html={JSON.stringify(galleryImages)} />
      </section>

      <section id="about" class="about">
        <div>
          <h2>Locally Owned Landscaping Service</h2>
          <p>
            Lakeside Landscaping LLC is focused on honest communication, reliable scheduling,
            and clean outdoor work. Whether you need routine lawn care, a seasonal cleanup,
            landscaping help, or snow removal, we help keep your property looking its best.
          </p>
          <br />
          <p>
            We work with residential and commercial customers and provide practical outdoor
            property care for lawns, planting beds, yards, walkways, and seasonal weather needs.
          </p>

          <ul class="about-list">
            <li>✓ Local service in Morris County and surrounding areas</li>
            <li>✓ Free estimates available</li>
            <li>✓ Lawn, landscape, cleanup, and snow services</li>
            <li>✓ Residential and commercial work</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="about-logo-wrap">
          <img src={logo} alt="Lakeside Landscaping LLC logo" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="400" height="400" />
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="area" class="service-area">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Service Area</h2>
          <p>
            Serving residential and commercial customers in Morris County and surrounding
            areas in New Jersey.
          </p>
          <div class="towns">
            Morris County, NJ and nearby New Jersey communities.
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="faq" class="faq">
        <div class="section-title">
          <h2>Common Questions</h2>
          <p>Helpful information before requesting an estimate.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-grid">
          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you offer free estimates?</h3>
            <p>Yes. Contact Lakeside Landscaping LLC by phone, text, or email to request a free estimate for your property.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>Do you work with both homes and businesses?</h3>
            <p>Yes. We provide lawn care, landscaping, cleanups, and seasonal services for residential and commercial properties.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="faq-item">
            <h3>What services are available seasonally?</h3>
            <p>Seasonal services include leaf removal, property cleanups, planting, mulch work, and snow removal during winter weather.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>Contact Us for a Free Estimate</h2>
        <p>
          Call, text, or email Lakeside Landscaping LLC to schedule lawn mowing,
          landscaping, cleanups, hardscaping, leaf removal, or snow removal services.
        </p>

        <div class="contact-info">
          <p><strong>Owner:</strong> {ownerName}</p>
          <p><strong>Phone:</strong> <a href={`tel:${phoneHref}`}>{phone}</a></p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href={`mailto:${email}`}>{email}</a></p>

          <div class="contact-actions">
            <a class="contact-button" href={`tel:${phoneHref}`}>Call or Text</a>
            <a class="review-button" href={reviewLink} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
              Leave a Google Review
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      © {new Date().getFullYear()} {businessName}. All rights reserved. Serving {location}.
    </footer>

    <script>
      const galleryDataElement = document.querySelector("#gallery-data");
      const slideshow = document.querySelector("#project-slideshow");

      if (galleryDataElement && slideshow) {
        const galleryImages = JSON.parse(galleryDataElement.textContent || "[]");
        const mainImage = document.querySelector("#main-slide-image");
        const mainLink = document.querySelector("#main-slide-link");
        const title = document.querySelector("#slide-title");
        const description = document.querySelector("#slide-description");
        const count = document.querySelector("#slide-count");
        const dots = Array.from(slideshow.querySelectorAll(".dot"));
        const prevButton = slideshow.querySelector(".slider-arrow.prev");
        const nextButton = slideshow.querySelector(".slider-arrow.next");

        let currentSlide = 0;

        function showSlide(index) {
          if (!galleryImages.length || !mainImage || !mainLink) return;

          currentSlide = (index + galleryImages.length) % galleryImages.length;
          const activeImage = galleryImages[currentSlide];

          mainImage.setAttribute("src", activeImage.src);
          mainImage.setAttribute("alt", activeImage.alt);
          mainLink.setAttribute("href", activeImage.src);

          if (title) title.textContent = activeImage.title;
          if (description) description.textContent = activeImage.description;
          if (count) count.textContent = `Photo ${currentSlide + 1} of ${galleryImages.length}`;

          dots.forEach((dot, dotIndex) => {
            dot.classList.toggle("active", dotIndex === currentSlide);
          });
        }

        prevButton?.addEventListener("click", () => showSlide(currentSlide - 1));
        nextButton?.addEventListener("click", () => showSlide(currentSlide + 1));

        dots.forEach((dot) => {
          dot.addEventListener("click", () => {
            const index = Number(dot.getAttribute("data-slide-index"));
            showSlide(index);
          });
        });

        document.addEventListener("keydown", (event) => {
          if (event.key === "ArrowLeft") showSlide(currentSlide - 1);
          if (event.key === "ArrowRight") showSlide(currentSlide + 1);
        });
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
